          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-59429cfbd7a22e41",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Mortgages\nEvery company works a little differently and figuring out the separate processes can be time consuming. We\u2019re here to lend a hand. The following tips on submitting new business will help keep things simple and make the process as quick and easy as possible.\nIf you\u2019re new to our Mortgage Broker Program, please contact one of our business development representatives or a client service representative at 1\u2011800\u2011263\u20118349 .\nReview our portfolio of mortgage products to determine which option best suits your client\u2019s needs.\nReview our application workflow to better understand our submission process.\nSubmit your client\u2019s application electronically.\nIf approved, all required documentation should be faxed to 1\u2011877\u2011812\u20118839.\nPRODUCTS\nB2B Bank Loans\nMortgages\nSavings\nInvestment accounts\nRATES\nGICs\nLoan rates\nMortgage rates\nBanking rates\nTOOLS\nCalculators\nForms\nMarketing material\nRESOURCES",
