          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-e13e7bb50f31d4a8",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "How many transactions do you get with the Blue Rewards Chequing Account?\nWith the Blue Rewards\u202fChequing Account, you get unlimited transactions *52 per month. When you move money out of your account \u2013 like an ATM withdrawal, bill payment or pre-authorized payment \u2013 that counts as a transaction. Money coming into your account \u2013 like payroll direct deposits or cash deposits at an ATM \u2013 don\u2019t count as transactions.\nWith the\nBlue Rewards\u202fChequing Account, you get unlimited transactions\nper month.\nWhen you move money out of your account \u2013 like an\nATM\nwithdrawal, bill payment or pre-authorized payment \u2013 that counts as a transaction. Money coming into your account \u2013 like payroll direct deposits or cash deposits at an\nATM\n\u2013 don\u2019t count as transactions.\nHow do I open a Blue Rewards Chequing Account online? You can open an Blue Rewards\u202fChequing Account online . You don\u2019t need an existing BMO",
