          "evidence_text_excerpt": "How do I sign up for the Overdraft Transfer Service?\nBook an appointment at a branch or contact customer care at 1-877-225-5266 .\nWhat does it cost to have the Overdraft Transfer Service? There is a $5 fee charged per transfer. Funds are transferred the next business day and the fee is charged when the transfer is completed. Note: The Overdraft Transfer Service fee is waived if you have selected the Premium Plan and for customers with the Student and Recent Graduate or Seniors Discounted Banking.",
