          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Youth/Student chequing accounts\nCreated for those under the age of majority, youth chequing accounts have no monthly fees until you turn 18. After that point, you can switch to a student account which typically has low or no monthly fees, unlimited transactions, access to student programs and other benefits.",
