          "field_name": "eligibility_text",
          "candidate_value": "You can earn up to $900.00 in total cash bonuses when you open a new Canadian Dollar Primary Chequing Account (\u201cChequing Account\u201d) with an Eligible Bank Plan (defined below), open a new Savings Amplifier Account (\u201cSavings Account\u201d) at any BMO Bank of Montreal branch or online at ",
